A lone figure stands atop a misty mountain peak at twilight, their silhouette radiating soft golden light from within, arms slightly outstretched as if embracing the cosmos above. The sky transitions from deep indigo to warm amber, filled with swirling nebulae and countless stars that seem to spiral downward like gentle rain, some stars appearing to flow into and through the figure's form. The warrior wears flowing robes that blend seamlessly with wisps of stardust and cloud. Their stance is peaceful yet powerful, grounded on ancient stone while connected to the infinite universe above. Rendered in Studio Ghibli style with soft watercolor textures, dreamy atmospheric perspective, and luminous color gradients that evoke wonder and quiet strength.
